  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink19-kilavi">
        <p type="edition"> paṉṉāḷ avaṉ cēṇiṭaip piriyavum āṟṟiyuḷaiyākiya nī ciṉṉāḷ avaṉ
          puṟattoḻukukiṉṟa itaṟku āṟṟāyākiṉṟatu eṉṉai? eṉṟa tōḻikku etirppāṭiṉṟi ōrūrkaṇṇē
          uṟaikaiyiṉālē āṟṟēṉākiṉṟēṉ eṉat talaimakaḷ colliyatu. </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink19">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> ekkar māattup putuppūm peruñciṉai</l>
          <l> puṇarntōr meymmaṇaṅ kamaḻun taṇpoḻil</l>
          <l> vēḻa veṇpū veḷḷuḷai cīkku</l>
          <l> mūra ṉākaliṟ kalaṅki</l>
          <l> māri malariṟ kaṇpaṉi yukumē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Distressed because of the man from the village</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the white manes of white wild cane flowers sweep across</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> the groves – cool and fragrant with the fusion/fragrance of bodies of
            those united </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> under the great, new-flowering branches of mango trees [growing] by
            the dunes –</l>
          <l> Tears are shed from [my] eyes, which are like blossoms in a shower.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
